'''Leila Nakabira''', na '''Leilah Nakabira''' (wavutse 1993) ni umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri Uganda, akaba Umwanditsi wafilimi  <ref name="AW">https://www.rfi.fr/en/africa/20190731-you-dont-need-validation-just-do-it-ugandan-actress-african-womens-day-message</ref>  n’umugore uharanira inyungu z'igitsinagore. <ref>https://www.sqoop.co.ug/201902/four-one-one/curvy-sexy-ugandan-women-named-new-tourist-attraction.html?fb_comment_id=2276607449070492_2278647982199772</ref> Ni umuyobozi mukuru wa Lepa Africa Films akaba yarashinze Leilah Nakabira For Charity Foundation. <ref name="K">https://mbu.ug/2019/11/05/fingers-crossed-leilah-nakabira-kenya-bound-for-lipff-awards/</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Nakabira yize Quantitative Economics muri kaminuza ya Makerere, Kampala, [[Ubugande|Uganda]], ari naho yarangirije. Nyuma yigihe runaka mubikorwa bya firime, yahisemo gusubira kwiga amashusho. <ref>https://www.monitor.co.ug/Magazines/Jobs-Career/Formal-training-qualifications-add-depth-your-natural-talents/689848-5455320-40g6ka/index.html</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yakiriye ibihembo bitatu byumukinnyi ''mwiza wa Zahabu (Ikinamico)'', ''Umukinnyi wa'' Zahabu wizewe cyane na ''Golden Discovery Actor'' ibihembo byigihembo cya Golden Movie Awards Africa 2018 (GMAA) cyabaye ku ya 2 kamena, amazina yabatowe yitwa Palaise de la culture, Treichville, Abidjan, [[Kote Divuwari|Côte d'Ivoire]], kubera filime yakinnye yitwa, ''The Forbidden'', yakozwe na Nampala Claire. <ref>https://mbu.ug/2018/05/23/leilah-nakabira-nominated-thrice-in-the-2018-golden-movie-awards/</ref> <ref>https://m.scoopernews.com/2018/05/21/2018-golden-movie-awards-africa-nominations-announced/862362</ref> Mu Zulu Afurika Film Academy Awards (ZAFAA) 2018, arabyuka bahatanira mu ''Best Actor Female'' category kuko filime imwe. <ref>https://doberre.com/ugandan-film-the-forbidden-sweeps-four-nominations-in-uk-based-film-awards-zafaa/</ref> Yari bahatanira na yegukanye ''Best Actress'' igihembo mu Film Festival Awards UDADA y'abagore yabereye ku ya 20 Ukwakira, 2018 muri Kenya kuko filime imwe. <ref>https://mbu.ug/2018/10/22/leilah-nakabira-bags-first-award-at-the-udada-film-festival/</ref> Yari yongeye bahatanira mu ''Best Actress'' category ku African Film Festival (Arta'atu) Awards 2019, kuko filime imwe. Ibirori byabaye ku ya 30 Kamena muri salle ya Moody Performance, 2520 Street Street, Dallas, Texas, [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|Amerika]] . <ref>https://glimug.com/leila-nakabira-diana-nabatanzi-nominated-african-film-festival-awards-us/</ref> <ref>https://mbu.ug/2019/07/03/leila-nakabira-and-claire-nampala-win-big-at-taff-awards-in-usa/</ref> Kuko hasigaye film imwe, mu kiyaga cya International Film Festival (LIPFF) Awards yabereye Ugushyingo 6-9, 2019 mu [[Kenya]], yari ku rutonde byiciro bibiri igihembo: ''Best Child bakoze'' na ''Best Actress.'' 

Mu munsi w’abagore muri Afurika 2019, yagiriye inama abagore kutagira ubwoba bakurikirana intego zabo. 

